OL,7,FAccording to reports, beer, wine and
OL,8,Fkebabs were served to guests which
OL,9,Fsome British Hindus saw as a "lack of
OL,10,Funderstanding or respect" for the
OL,11,Fsacred religious traditions associated
OL,12,Fwith Diwali.
OL,14,FThe event prompted complaints from
OL,15,Fsome Hindus, including Conservative MP
OL,16,FShivani Raja, who said the
OL,17,Fcelebrations "were overshadowed by a
OL,18,Fdisappointing ignorance to the customs
OL,19,Fof many British Hindus", adding that
OL,20,Fshe was "deeply saddened".
