OL,7,FInsight UK, a social movement for
OL,8,FBritish Hindus and Indians, previously
OL,9,Fsaid it had also written to Downing
OL,10,FStreet to complain about the event
OL,11,Fafter hearing Hindu guests who
OL,12,Fattended "reportedly expressed their
OL,13,Fshock and dismay at being served meat
OL,14,Fand alcohol".
OL,16,FHinduism does not prohibit alcohol or
OL,17,Fmeat but many Hindus traditionally do
OL,18,Fnot consume alcohol during Diwali -
OL,19,Fthe "festival of lights" - and a large
OL,20,Fmajority only eat vegetarian food.
