OL,7,FA Number 10 spokesperson said: "The
OL,8,FPrime Minister was pleased to welcome
OL,9,Fa range of communities celebrating
OL,10,FDiwali to a reception in Downing
OL,11,FStreet.
OL,13,F"He paid tribute to the huge
OL,14,Fcontribution the British Hindu, Sikh &
OL,15,FJain communities make to our country
OL,16,Fand how the government is driven by
OL,17,Fthe shared values of hard work,
OL,18,Fambition and aspiration.
