OL,7,F"A mistake was made in the
OL,8,Forganisation of the event. We
OL,9,Funderstand the strength of feeling on
OL,10,Fthis issue and so would apologise to
OL,11,Fthe community and assure them it will
OL,12,Fnot happen again."
OL,14,FBoth Raja and Insight UK had pointed
OL,15,Fto the fact that no meat or alcohol
OL,16,Fwere served during celebrations last
OL,17,Fyear while Rishi Sunak, who became the
OL,18,Fcountry's first-ever Hindu prime
OL,19,Fminister, was in office.
