OL,7,FOther attendees say the celebrations
OL,8,Fhave always been alcohol and meat-
OL,9,Ffree, including before Sunak's tenure.
OL,11,F"Diwali is not just a time for
OL,12,Ffestivity, but also holds a deeply
OL,13,Freligious meaning," Insight UK wrote
OL,14,Fon X at the time. "The sacred festival
OL,15,Fof Diwali emphasizes purity and
OL,16,Fdevotion and hence traditionally
OL,17,Finvolves vegetarian meals and strict
OL,18,Favoidance of alcohol.
