OL,7,F"The choice of menu at the Diwali
OL,8,Fcelebration hosted by the Prime
OL,9,FMinister himself, displays an
OL,10,Fappalling lack of understanding or
OL,11,Frespect for the religious traditions
OL,12,Fassociated with with the festival of
OL,13,FDiwali."
OL,15,FRaja and Insight UK welcomed the fact
OL,16,FDowning Street apologised and said
OL,17,Fthey hoped to work together in the
OL,18,Ffuture to advise on Hindu cultural
OL,19,Fsensitivities.
